</p>

<h2>Monthsary vs Anniversary: What's the Difference?</h2>

<p>
  A <strong>monthsary</strong> celebrates the same calendar day each <em>month</em>. An <strong>anniversary</strong> celebrates the same calendar day each <em>year</em>. Both share the same start date — the day you began your relationship.
</p>

