<h2>Quick Recap</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Count by calendar day, not 30-day blocks.</li>
  <li>Same day, next month = 1 month.</li>
  <li>Don't count the day you started as "month one complete."</li>
  <li>For short months (Feb), use the last day of the month.</li>
</ul>

